title: Skinning My Phone Case With Leather - Leather Craft

meta.description:
In this leather craft video I make a tooled leather skin for my cell phone case. The skin has an added card pocket that comes in handy for the times when I may not want to carry both a phone and a wallet. Cell phone cases are just another place that can be a blank canvas for custom leather work. I hope you enjoy the video and get inspired to customize your own case.
